                        </summary>
                        <div class="faq-answer-content">
                            <p>Administered locally by the Institute of Chartered Accountants of Nepal (ICAN), the track demands a structural progression across CAP-I foundation, CAP-II intermediate fields, and final CAP-III testing parameters alongside 3 mandatory years of practical firm articleship training.</p>
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

